{"_path":"/construction/c34","_dir":"construction","_draft":false,"_partial":false,"_locale":"","title":"樂捷段社會住宅","description":null,"image":"/images/construction/c34-4.jpeg","sequence":34,"category":"社會住宅","status":"2.施工","type":null,"budget":null,"link":null,"head":{"meta":[{"name":"keywords","content":""},{"name":"robots","content":""},{"name":"author","content":""},{"name":"copyright","content":"© 2024 A7新林口-社區網站"},{"name":"og:title","content":"地方行政"}]},"publishedAt":"2028-12-31T00:00:00.000Z","toc":true,"body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"樂捷段社會住宅"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"樂捷段社會住宅"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"計畫概要"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"計畫概要"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"項目 樂捷段社會住宅"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"類別 居住環境 - CON-34"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"完工 2028"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"經費 44 億"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"狀態 施工"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://money.udn.com/money/story/7307/8191443"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"經濟日報 2024/08/28"}]},{"type":"text","value":":\n內政部國家住宅及都市更新中心 2024/08/28 舉辦桃園市龜山區「樂善安居」社會住宅動土典禮，提供 790 戶住宅單元，預計 2028 年竣工。總工程經費約 44 億 1370 萬元，由中央全額投資興建，是中央在桃園市動土的第 6 案社會住宅。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"「樂善安居」位於龜山區文南路，鄰近中華郵政物流中心、樂善科技園區、華亞科技園區、文青國民中小學。開車 5 分鐘可抵達機場捷運站 A7 體育大學站，10 分鐘可上國道一號林口交流道，交通相當便利。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"「樂善安居」基地面積達 1 公頃，建築規模為地上 14 層、地下 3 層，有 ABCD 四棟，低樓層設置托嬰中心、店鋪等商業設施，留設綠帶與戶外開放空間，服務在地鄰里居民，提供優質居住與友善照護的宜居環境。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"國家住都中心與桃園市政府在短時間內完成土地取得與建築規劃設計，積極推動「樂善安居」社宅成為龜山區內最大的社會住宅，目前桃園市內的社會住宅，在六都中排名第五，呼籲桃園市若有更多國、公有土地，也能釋放出來，讓國家住都中心新建更多社會住宅，符合桃園市人口愈來愈多的需求。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://sh.hurc.org.tw/H/H-333-001?fbclid=IwY2xjawE70-dleHRuA2FlbQIxMAABHb4R8HkXhF3Q6oOnksx-PQ-D6b2b8KRqT02XQLanTSqnPT8DmesAuvCAwQ_aem_-1HVWvfNu6_L9-4jXN2izA"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"國家住宅及都市更新中心 網站"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"基本資訊"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n基地面積： 10824.81 平方公尺"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n總戶數：790 戶"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n房型規劃："}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"套房 / 492 戶"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"二房型 / 246 戶"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"三房型 / 52 戶"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"附屬設施：托嬰中心"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n興辦進度：簽約日期 / 112 年 7 月 25 日"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://tw.news.yahoo.com/a7%E7%A7%91%E6%8A%80%E5%9C%92%E5%8D%80%E6%97%81%E6%A8%82%E5%96%84%E5%AE%89%E5%B1%85%E7%A4%BE%E5%AE%85-%E7%B5%B1%E5%8C%85%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%E6%B1%BA%E6%A8%99-121732491.html"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Yahoo!新聞 2023/06/28"}]},{"type":"text","value":":\n傅沁怡／台北報導\n2023 年 6 月 28 日\n"},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://www.hurc.org.tw/hurc/docDetail?uid=17&pid=10&doc_id=1265"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"國家住宅及都市更新中心"}]},{"type":"text","value":" 於桃園市龜山區的「樂善安居」社會住宅新建統包工程 2023/06/28 日決標，將由「三民營造股份有限公司、開鎰水電有限公司、恩典聯合建築師事務所」統包團隊共同攜手打造，預計 2028 年完工，為桃園市再提供 790 戶社宅。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"該案為龜山首案社宅決標，加上本案後，國家住都中心於桃園市已決標 2,805 戶社宅，全台累積已完工及已決標社宅共 3 萬 6,076 戶。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"「樂善安居」社宅基地面積達 1 公頃，位於龜山區文南路，鄰近中華郵政物流中心、樂善科技園區、華亞科技園區、泰山工業區，車行 5 分鐘即可抵達機場捷運站 A7 體育大學站、樂善國小，距離國道一號林口交流道僅十分鐘車程。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"建設詳情"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"建設詳情"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"龜山樂捷段社會住宅"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"c34-4.jpeg","src":"/images/construction/c34-4.jpeg"},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"c34-2.jpeg","src":"/images/construction/c34-2.jpeg"},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"c34-1.jpeg","src":"/images/construction/c34-1.jpeg"},"children":[]}]}],"toc":{"title":"","searchDepth":2,"depth":2,"links":[{"id":"樂捷段社會住宅","depth":2,"text":"樂捷段社會住宅","children":[{"id":"計畫概要","depth":3,"text":"計畫概要"},{"id":"建設詳情","depth":3,"text":"建設詳情"}]}]}},"_type":"markdown","_id":"content:construction:c34.md","_source":"content","_file":"construction/c34.md","_extension":"md"}